# This repository exposes ONLY the BetterCR extension (the improved rewrite of
# BetterCrunchyroll) plus its landing files. Everything else stays on disk
# locally but is untracked / hidden from git & GitHub.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/BetterCR/
!/README.md
!/README.en.md
# Docs: expose only the README screenshots, hide the private API notes.
!/docs/
/docs/*
!/docs/screenshots/
